MatrixCodeGrid
--------------

"MatrixCodeGrid" is an impressive piece of code that recreates the visual effect of falling lines from "The Matrix" on your Linux or macOS terminal. Customizable and captivating, the code lines flow and fade, providing a hypnotic and visually stunning experience. Transform your shell with just a few lines of code and immerse yourself in the world of "The Matrix." (Note: caution is advised when using it in critical work environments.)

--
sudo pacman -S ncurses
--
gcc -o matrixcode matrixcode.c -lncurses
